statements.sql:
SELECT sc.id, c.parent_id, count(*) as total
FROM posts as a
INNER JOIN categories as sc ON sc.id=a.category_id AND sc.active=1
INNER JOIN categories as c ON c.id=sc.parent_id AND c.active=1
WHERE a.country_code = 'KE' AND (a.verified_email=1 AND a.verified_phone=1) AND a.archived!=1 AND a.deleted_at IS NULL
GROUP BY sc.id
hints: The != operator is not standard. Use the <> operator to test for inequality instead.

statements.sql:
SELECT cat.id, SUM(total) as total
FROM ((SELECT c.id as id, count(*) as total
FROM posts as a
INNER JOIN categories as c ON c.id=a.category_id AND c.active=1
WHERE a.country_code = 'KE' AND (a.verified_email=1 AND a.verified_phone=1) AND a.archived!=1 AND a.deleted_at IS NULL
GROUP BY c.id) UNION ALL (SELECT c.id as id, count(*) as total
FROM posts as a
INNER JOIN categories as sc ON sc.id=a.category_id AND sc.active=1
INNER JOIN categories as c ON c.id=sc.parent_id AND c.active=1
WHERE a.country_code = :countryCode AND (a.verified_email=1 AND a.verified_phone=1) AND a.archived!=1 AND a.deleted_at IS NULL
GROUP BY c.id)) cat
GROUP BY cat.id
hints: The != operator is not standard. Use the <> operator to test for inequality instead.

statements.sql:
SELECT count(*) as total FROM (SELECT DISTINCT a.*, py.package_id as py_package_id
FROM posts as a
INNER JOIN categories as c ON c.id=a.category_id AND c.active=1
LEFT JOIN categories as cp ON cp.id=c.parent_id AND cp.active=1
LEFT JOIN (SELECT MAX(id) max_id, post_id FROM payments WHERE active=1 GROUP BY post_id) mpy ON mpy.post_id = a.id AND a.featured=1
LEFT JOIN payments as py ON py.id=mpy.max_id
LEFT JOIN packages as p ON p.id=py.package_id
WHERE a.country_code = 'KE' AND (a.verified_email = 1 AND a.verified_phone = 1) AND a.archived != 1 AND a.deleted_at IS NULL
ORDER BY p.lft DESC, a.created_at DESC) as x
hints: The != operator is not standard. Use the <> operator to test for inequality instead.

statements.sql:
SELECT DISTINCT a.*, py.package_id as py_package_id
FROM posts as a
INNER JOIN categories as c ON c.id=a.category_id AND c.active=1
LEFT JOIN categories as cp ON cp.id=c.parent_id AND cp.active=1
LEFT JOIN (SELECT MAX(id) max_id, post_id FROM payments WHERE active=1 GROUP BY post_id) mpy ON mpy.post_id = a.id AND a.featured=1
LEFT JOIN payments as py ON py.id=mpy.max_id
LEFT JOIN packages as p ON p.id=py.package_id
WHERE a.country_code = 'KE' AND (a.verified_email = 1 AND a.verified_phone = 1) AND a.archived != 1 AND a.deleted_at IS NULL
ORDER BY p.lft DESC, a.created_at DESC
LIMIT 0, 12
